You may give the following commands to your followers:

release <name> - Allows you to release your follower early,
   in case (for instance) you wish to charm a different
   animal or conjure a different elemental.
dismiss <name> - Same as 'release'.
secure <name> - Stops other people from taking items your
   followers are carrying.
allow <name> - Allows other people to take items your
   followers are carrying.
unleash <target> - Causes your follower to attack the target,
   assuming the target is valid (PK checks, etc., apply.)
heel - Causes your follower to stop fighting.
toggle - Sets whether or not your follower automatically helps
   you in combat.
